          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <h1>The festivities arenâ€™t over!</h1>
          <p class='major'>You are cordially invited to spend the evening with us at a  festive dinner.</p>
          <p><b style='color: red;'>Please note that the organisation of this event may differ according to health restrictions.</b></p>
          <p><i>At 7:30 pm &ndash; Salle communale, 2 Route de la Biolle, 73200 Pallud</i></p>
          <ul class="actions stacked">
            <li><a href="#first" class="button large wide smooth-scroll-middle">Here's my answer!</a></li>
